**v.1.0.0**

# refsproj1 — Multi-API BibTeX tools


Fetch BibTeX from [arXiv](https://arxiv.org/), [Crossref](https://www.crossref.org/), or [Semantic Scholar](https://www.semanticscholar.org/) and optionally annotate Markdown with numbered citations.

**Commands**

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| **`bulk`** | API search → one `.bib` or many (split by title, optional session folder). Supports arXiv, Crossref, Semantic Scholar, or **all** (merged). |
| **`match`** | Fuzzy title search → pick one hit → one `.bib`. Choose your API with `--api`. |
| **`smart`** | Chunk a `.md` file → search per chunk → `[1][2]…` in text + `## References` + optional BibTeX. Multi-API support. |

**Run:** `python app.py …` from `refsproj1`, or `app.bat …` on Windows. Python must resolve the `src` package (run from project root or set `PYTHONPATH`).

